# Zero Fluff & Real Data

Promoted from `.agents/rules/zero-fluff.md` + `no-false-data.md`.

## Data

- **No** `MOCK_DATA`, hardcoded dashboard counts, or fake API responses in production UI
- If a number isn't from API → fix backend or show empty/loading — never invent
- Mutations: optimistic `setQueryData` + invalidate related query keys

## Language

Use plain English in user-facing copy (not "Execute Batch CSV Mutation" → "Upload Lead List").

## Loading

No stale-data flicker — validate cache/loading before rendering metrics.
